{
  "name": "RPlog_Poisoning_Incident",
  "title": "Poisoning Incident",
  "summary": "At the Grand Palanhi Hotel, the academy-trained young man Jusre lingers on the balcony beside the laconic, cigarra-smoking Vermillion while Roark slips into a guest room from which strained, desperate voices are briefly heard. After the hotel manager and staff discover a guest dead of apparent poisoning, a shaken Jusre overhears talk of suicide and authorities, and hurries downstairs to warn his companion Alexis. In the lobby, where Dillon presides over a tense gathering that also includes Runther, Piper, Kuxli, Roark and the protocol droid C3PO, news of the death ripples through the group as Jusre, sickened, is repeatedly ill and is comforted by Alexis. Vermillion quietly works the room, eavesdropping on the manager's harried conversation with Dillon, while the manager publicly insists it was only a small mishap being handled by the authorities. Unsettled and increasingly paranoid, the guests trade uneasy speculation before drifting off, Jusre and others resolving to leave the hotel for the night.",
